<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yǒu yī jù huà wǒ men yǒng yuǎn yào shuō 迦南212</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu yī jù huà wǒ men yǒng yuǎn yào shuō fú yīn hé xuān jiào lián zhe wǒ men de mài bó
 tiān shàng de gōng wǒ men qí xīn yào qù zuò tóng chàng yī shǒu xiàng qián jìn de gē
 qiān shān wàn shuǐ jiǎo xià guò yǒu yǎn lèi xiào shēng huī huáng hé qū zhé
 dà de yě zài hē cǎi yǒng wǎng mò tuì suō jīn tiān dé dào de bǐ zuó tiān gèng duō.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>212</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>